{"tid":139193,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「郭Sir」轉工了！去民眾再搞網台：我會教大家健身","createTime":"2017-03-01T08:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T17:00:28.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38a9751d90a1611175b2d099fb3439e5e73cde74","tid":139193,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T08:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/01/163247_0a92a550aad603b25871bbf88800cb39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F01%2F163247_0a92a550aad603b25871bbf88800cb39.jpg&h=1fc7cb3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「股壇大隻佬」郭思治（郭sir）之前同耀才（1428）「分手」後，都冇人知佢轉去邊間。唔使估估下，今日民眾金融（279）旗下民眾證券公佈，請到郭Sir加盟，出任董事總經理一職。<br />\n<br />\n民眾證券仲講明，會籌辦一個網台製作財經節目，喺民眾證券個App度播放。郭sir就話，網台以內地同香港觀眾目標比例，會係七比三，所以節目會係普通話、廣東話都有齊，「咁依家有滬港通、深港通，內地投資者係天文數字，所以一定放多啲資源喺內地。」<br />\n<br />\n佢話，佢自己啱啱返工，公司租埋中銀40樓全層去做網台，連埋裝修、請人等工作，相信最快要三個月先推出。至於節目方面，佢就話希望做到交易時段全天侯播放，更特別嘅係，除咗有一般傳統財經節目外，「拍大約十集，講吓健身、點樣減肥、點樣Fit啲，我就親自喺鏡頭前示範。」佢話，今朝返到公司，收到好多人祝賀，「我只係覆WhatsApp都覆咗成個幾鐘。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56369728&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56369728%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170301&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=0127739d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56369728%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170301&h=5aa3e98c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56369728&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170301</a><br />\n<br />\n//郭sir係財演中叫做好啲㗎啦，以前係電視見佢解答c9電話，都唔係完全老點，有啲point"},{"pid":"26f27789ecd9a2f72fa6a4b77efebab4b4a17ab2","tid":139193,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日睇佢市後5分鐘短評，日日都講同樣野"},{"pid":"b268239daff90e938c4697c2283f3477048df120","tid":139193,"uid":62587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:29:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日睇佢市後5分鐘短評，日日都講同樣野</blockquote><br />\n好廢 講左等於冇講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67d03981350c746b51e34b7c070c6cdac3ff212","tid":139193,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"有無佢同李小龍打嘅片睇"},{"pid":"cd970b5f2e4fd5fd62596935bbea56dc78f4714d","tid":139193,"uid":68118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:23:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日睇佢市後5分鐘短評，日日都講同樣野</blockquote><br />\n1000點波幅已經係滿足成個月<br />\n仲係續沉頂 續沉底格局<br />\n先高後低 先低後高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5029afd8004e829cabe663d9da909cc607dfb34","tid":139193,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"大師好玩好多"},{"pid":"9a5932b566d043414f945da178495e902e30edd3","tid":139193,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大師好玩好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然啦!<br />\n師父D奇幻潮<br />\n我睇少日都流口水鼻涕<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/dbba79.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fdbba79.gif&h=1b6c6da2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2d5e839daef1e2cb6a827cc1e625e6091cd74ee","tid":139193,"uid":12554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/